    <h3><a href="#">Getting started</a></h3>
    <p>Drive is easy to install on alot of setups, it's as simple as running ```go get github.com/odeke-em/drive``` provided you have golang installed <a href="#">more info here</a>. You can also install drive with a few prebuilt packages, or it might even be available in your distros repos already <a href="#">more deatils here</a>.</p>
  </div>
